OMWATSI W’OKWA KIDIPA | BUSANA NAKI YESU MWAGHALHWA N’ERIHOLHA ?
Omo mwaka owa 33 E.K . , Yesu we Nazareti mw’ithibwa .
Mubamuhangirira ambu ni mughobya , bamamuswirya kutsibu , n’erimukongomerera okwa muthi .
Aliwe Nyamuhanga mwamulhubukya , kandi habere hakya biro 40 , Yesu mwahethukira elhubulha .
Omwatsi oyu thukabanagho omwa bitabu bbini eby’Enjiri eby’Amasako w’Ekigiriki , awakanahulhawa mwa Endaghano Embyaka .
( 1 Abanya Korinto 15 : 14 ) Aliwe emyatsi eyo kwenene yamabya imuyabya , kwesi abandu ibakendibya ibalindirire omughulhu owuwene , nawu ogho wangana sangiramo .
Neryo ebiri omwa bitabu by’Enjiri , nina kwenene kutse ni ngano buyira ?
Erithendibya ng’esyongano buyira , abakasekulhaya emyatsi bakalhangira ndeke - ndeke ebiri omwa bitabu by’Enjiri ini kwenene .
Ng’eky’erileberyako muli amena w’emyanya eyinasibwe , eyineho namunabwire .
Yikathubwira okwa bandu abanabyaho , kandi n’abakasoma ebya kera bakalighirana n’ekyo . ​ — Luka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Yesu nibya anakanibirweko omwa bitabu by’abandu b’ekihugho eby’omwa kighonye ky’erimbere n’ekyakabiri .
* Emibere ithirawamo ngoku kiri omwa bitabu by’Enjiri yihambene ndeke n’emibere Abaroma babya bak’ithira mw’abandu omwa buthuku obo .
N’ekindi , emyatsi eyabya eyi yihandikire omwa mibere ey’okwenene n’ey’erithendi bisirira ​ — nibya n’erikania okwa bisobyo by’abigha ba Yesu .
( Matayo 26 : 56 ; Luka 22 : 24 - 26 ; Yoane 18 : 10 , 11 ) Ebyosi ebi bikakanganaya ndeke - ndeke ngoku abahandika Enjiri mubakolesya okwenene bakahandika ebihambire oku Yesu .
Nomwakinasibwe ehosi ngoku Yesu mwabyaho kandi amaholha , abandi ibangana bugha bathi mw’athalhubuka .
Nibya n’abakwenda biwe mubanatsuka erithika - thika bakowa ambu abirilhubuka .
( Luka 24 : 11 ) Erithika - thika lyosi eryo mulyahwa omughulhu ibo n’abandi bigha balholha oku Yesu iniabirilhubuka .
Okwa buthuku bughuma , abandu nga 500 mubanamulholhako iniabirilhubuka . ​ — 1 Abanya Korinto 15 : 6 .
Abigha ba Yesu mubathulhughania buthubaha erilhubuka liwe okwa bandu abosi nibya n’okwa bamw’itha , nomwakine indi kyangalekire ibahambwa n’erithibwa .
( Emibiri 4 : 1 - 3 , 10 , 19 , 20 ; 5 : 27 - 32 ) Mbwino abigha banganabere n’obuthubaha obwosi obu isibakakasirye Yesu kw’abirilhubuka ?
Yesu eribya kwenene imwalhubuka , y’enzumwa eyaleka Ekikristayo ikyakanyirira okwa buthuku obo na munabwire .
Emyatsi eyihambire okwa lhuholho lhwa Yesu n’erilhubuka liwe eyiri omwa bitabu by’Enjiri yikalighirana ndeke n’ebihandikire ebya kera .
Eribisoma ndeke ikikendi leka iwakakasya ngoku emyatsi eyi muyabya .
Kandi erikakasya lyawu lyangana thasyaghuma wukayitheghererya ekyaleka ebyosi ebi ibyabya .
Tacitus , oyuwangabya iniabuthawa omwaka owa 55 E.K . , mwahandika athi : “ Kristo , oyulhuire kw’erina , [ Abakristayo ] , mwaghalhwa kutsibu omwa byalha bya Pontio Pilato omwa buthabali bwa Tiberio . ”
Yesu akathasyakanibawako na Suetonius ( ow’omwa kighonye ky’erimbere ) ; omusomi w’ebya kera Omuyuda , ye Josephus ( ow’omwa kighonye ky’erimbere ) ; na Pliny the Younger , omuthabali owe Bitinia ( okw’itsuka ly’ekighonye kyakabiri ) .
( 1 Petero 1 : 24 , 25 ) Nibya sikyanga thokekene ababya bakahakanisya Yesu erihandika bingyi ebyangalekire abandu ibamw’ikirirya .
Omughuma w’okwa bakwenda ba Yesu , ye Petero mwakania okw’ilhubuka lya Yesu athi : ‘ Nyamuhanga mwamulhubukya enyuma w’ebiro bisathu , kandi mwaleka inialholhwako , nikwa abandu bosi mubathamulholhako , ninathwe thwabya balhangiri abo Nyamuhanga ayisogha erimbere . Ithwe muthwalya n’eripulya haghuma nayu abirilhubuka okwa baholi . ’
Enjiri ya Matayo yikathubwira ngoku omughulhu abanya madini bowa ngoku Yesu abirilhubuka , mubalengaho eribulirania omwatsi oyo . ​ — Matayo 28 : 11 - 15 .
Mbwino eki kyamanyisaya kithi Yesu syabya anzire abandu bakaminya kw’abirilhubuka ?
Eyihi , kundi Petero mwathasyabugha athi : “ Yesu mwathuhana athi thukangiriraye engulhu yuwene okwa bandu n’erithulhagho kw’ali oyo Nyamuhanga ahira mwa mutsweri w’abaliho n’omutsweri w’abaholire . ”
Abakristayo b’okwenene babirikolha ekyo kandi banemulholha embere erikikolha . ​ — Emibiri 10 : 42 .
“ Ebibi mubyahika munakihugho busana n’omundu mughuma [ Adamu ] n’olhuholho lhwam’ingira busana n’ekibi kiwe . ” ​ — Abanya Roma 5 : 12
Iwukendi bugha wuthiki balyakubulhaya bathi , “ Wunanzire iwabyaho kera na kera ? ”
Abangyi ibakendi bugha bathi bananzire aliwe bathi si ky’amenge erilengekania wuthya .
Bakabugha bathi , omundu aliho ini w’erisyaholha .
Thuthabugha thuthi lero bamabulya bathi , “ Wunanzire eriholha ? ”
Abangyi ibakendi bugha bathi eyihi .
E Biblia yikakanganaya yithi Nyamuhanga mwahira omwa bandu mw’eryanza eribyaho .
Yikabugha yithi “ abirihira erikotha omwa muthima wabo . ” ​ — Omugambuli 3 : 11 .
Aliwe omwa kwenene , abandu sibalibyaho kera na kera .
Kutse , Nyamuhanga anawithe eky’akolire eryuwania ekyasobire ekyo ?
Erisubirya eriri omwa Biblia likatsemesaya , lihambire okwa kyaleka Yesu iniaghalhwa n’eriholha .
Esyasura isathu esy’erimbere omwa Biblia sikathubwira ngoku Nyamuhanga mwaha ababuthi bethu b’erimbere , Adamu na Eva , b’akaghisa ak’eribyaho kera na kera n’eribabwira ekya batholere erikolha erithoka eribyaho .
Kandi sikathasyasoborera ngoku balemawa eriowa Nyamuhanga n’eriherya akaghisa ako .
Omwatsi eribya iniakanibwe omwa bikuhi n’erihikira okwa nzumwa kikanaleka abandi ibabugha bathi ni lhughano buyira .
Aliwe , ng’ebitabu by’Enjiri , ekitabu ky’Enzuko nakyo kikakanganaya ngoku ebirimo ni by’okwenene .
Adamu erithendiowa Nyamuhanga mwabirilhwiririraki ?
E Biblia yikasubamu yithi : “ Ebibi mubyahika muna kihugho busana n’omundu mughuma [ Adamu ] , n’olhuholho mulhwingira busana n’ekibi kiwe , neryo lithya olhuholho mulhwahika okwa bandu bosi , kusangwa abosi mubakolha ebibi . ”
Neryo mwaherya amaha w’eribya n’engebe y’erikotha , n’erighunzerera mwaholha .
Thwabirisighalya ekibi kiwe kundi thulhuire omw’iyo .
Mbwino hane ekya Nyamuhanga abirikolha erithasyuwania emyatsi ?
Nyamuhanga mwahiraho emitheghekere ey’erisubulya kutse erithasyaghulha ekya Adamu abya iniabiriherya okwa baana biwe , ni bugha ambu , amaha w’eribyaho kera na kera .
Omwa Abanya Roma 6 : 23 , e Biblia yithi : “ Obuhingi bw’erikolha ebibi ni lhuholho . ”
Eki kikamanyisaya ngoku olhuholho lhwasa busana n’ekibi .
Nethu thukakolha ebibi neryo kandi ithwahikwako obuhingyi bw’ekibi , olhuholho .
Aliwe sithwe thwakolha ekibi ekyo , thwabuthirawa mukyo .
Busana n’olhwanzo , Nyamuhanga mwathuma Yesu , erithulihira ‘ obuhingi bw’ekibi . ’
Olhuholho lhwa Yesu lhukakyungulha enzira eyikakolhaya okwa ngebe y’erikotha ey’obutseme
Kundi omulhume mughuma , oyuhikene , Adamu , mwathulethara ekibi n’olhuholho busana n’obuthowa , muhayithaghisya owundi oyuhikene , omwowa erihika n’okwa lhuholho , erithulhamya okwa bikalhwiririra omwa kibi .
E Biblia yikasoborera eki yithi : “ Busana n’erithendiowa ly’omundu mughuma , abandu bangyi mubayirwa mwa bakakolha nabi , neryo lithya busana n’eriowa ly’omundu mughuma , abangyi basyayirwa mwa bathunganene . ”
Mwalhua elhubulha , amabya hano ng’omundu oyuhikene , * kandi amaholha omwa bwethu .
Ekyo kyabirileka ikyathokekana okw’ithwe eribya bathunganene embere sya Nyamuhanga n’eribya n’amaha w’erisyabana engebe y’erikotha .
Aliwe , busana naki mukyayithaghisya Yesu eriholha eriberererya eki ?
Nyamuhanga Omuthoki w’Ebyosi , mbwino syanga kwamir’ikyathwamu athi abaana ba Adamu babyeho kera na kera ?
Nyamuhanga kwa kilhusyaho , abandu bangabulire ng’angana kangania obulingirirania n’omwa yindi myatsi .
Ng’eky’erileberyako , bangabere bakabulha ng’anemwendi syathwamu ndeke nga ni bahi omwa baana ba Adamu abatholere erisyabana engebe y’erikotha .
Ibabulha ng’anemwendisya berererya n’emilhaghe yiwe .
Nyamuhanga erithwamu erikolesya obulingirirania omw’iletha omulhamu wethu , kikaleka ithwayikethera ngoku mughulhu wosi akakolha ebihikire .
Busana na Yesu eriholha , Nyamuhanga mwabya iniamakyungulira abandu b’enzira y’erisyabyaho kera na kera omwa kihugho Paradiso .
Th’owa ebinywe bya Yesu ebiri omu Yoane 3 : 16 : “ Nyamuhanga mwanza ekihugho ky’athya , kyaleka iniaha Mughalha wiwe , Ekyusa kiwe , neryo oyukamwikiriraya syahere , nikwa abye n’engebe y’erikotha . ”
Neryo kwesi olhuholho lhwa Yesu silhuli subulira okw’ikangania Nyamuhanga kw’ali w’obulingirirania , aliwe kutsibu - tsibu lhukakanganaya olhwanzo lhunene olhw’awithire abandu .
Aliwe ibbwa , mukyanayithaghisya Yesu eriaghalhwa n’eriholha omwa mibere y’erinuba athya , ngoku kikanibweko omwa bitabu by’Enjiri ?
Iyo eryingira omwa kirengesyo eky’obulhumi obukalire , kandi akasighalha iniane muthaleghulha , Yesu mwakangania amabehi awali omwa kya Sitani abugha athi abandu sibangabya batheleghulha oku Nyamuhanga bamabya omwa bitsibu .
( Yobu 2 : 4 , 5 ) Ebyo mubyabya nga ni kwenene omughulhu Sitani ingiraya Adamu oyuhikene y’omwa kibi .
Aliwe Yesu ​ — oyuwabya ahikene nga Adamu ​ — iyo mwabya mwowa nomwanabana eriaghalhwa erikalire .
( 1 Abanya Korinto 15 : 45 ) Neryo aho , mwakangania ngoku Adamu nayu kw’anza , ang’owire Nyamuhanga .
Omw’iyiyinia liwe , Yesu mwathusighira olhughobe lhw’erikwama .
( 1 Petero 2 : 21 ) Nyamuhanga mwahemba Mughalha wiwe busana n’obwowa bwiwe , omw’imuha engebe y’obuthaholha , elhubulha .
Yesu mwakangania eky’erikolha akabugha athi : “ Eyi ni ngebe y’erikotha , abandu bakuminye iwe Nyamuhanga mughuma w’okwenene , n’eriminya Yesu Kristo oyowathuma . ” ​ — Yoane 17 : 3 .
Abakahulhukaya egazeti eno bakakuhira mw’omuhwa w’erithasy’igha bingyi oku Yehova , Nyamuhanga w’okwenene , n’oku Mughalha wiwe Yesu Kristo .
